description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 min Gentle Yoga for Flexibility & Stress Reduction' from the channel Yoga with Kassandra.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let your stress melt away with this gentle yoga flow with full body stretches.

Hi everyone, thanks for joining me. I'm going to take you through this 15 minute hatha yoga class for flexibility and stress relief. This is a gentle soothing yoga class to help you relax and stretch your body, great for all experience levels. No props are required. We'll finish our class together with a few rounds of Box Breath - Sama Vritti Pranayama.

This can be a therapeutic yoga class to do when you're experiencing anxiety and want to ground yourself. We'll start with a bit of mindful breathing before going into our yoga poses. Enjoy!
